rch-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-c-2.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55r2-c-2","specFolder":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/C-rest-of-server","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"fanout-gpt55r2-c-2-1781761364358-6qni37","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55r2-c-2-1781761364358-6qni37\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55r2-c-2-1781761364358-6qni37\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt55r2-c-2-1781761364358-6qni37\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 227,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781761396015,"end":1781761396078}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_02eb84c966efdeef016a33856768b8819185096633a668fa4e"}},"id":"prt_ed9411bfa0017V11WGhGrF6iND","sessionID":"ses_126bf2c74ffeVn7GN2uRmNhN2M","messageID":"msg_ed940dc3a001LcWj8F80tWfHGx"}}
